strings: <voice_0x0100156B><se_def>awesome!: ...... They do not believe in ......! What can I...?
<voice_0x0100156F><se_def>exploding spikes: I've always been stubborn, but with your help, I can finally control this body in my own way.
<voice_0x01001570><se_def>exploding spikes: The foolish man called himself High Priest now. The seal is breaking because I don't have a last resort!
<voice_0x01001571><se_def>exploding spikes: Yes, it's time for a new life!
<voice_0x01001573><se_def>exploding spikes: Fix it! wake me up
